TiCarousel
===========================================

**TiCarousel** is an Appcelerator Titanium module which wraps iCarousel, a 
simple, highly customizable, data-driven 3D carousel for iOS and Mac OS.


Installation
------------

1. Copy the `com.obscure.ticarousel-iphone-1.0.zip` file to your $TITANIUM_HOME
directory (usually `~/Library/Application Support/Titanium`). 
1. Edit your project's `tiapp.xml` and add the module.  Example:
    <modules>
        <module platform="iphone" version="1.0">com.obscure.TiCarousel</module>
    </modules>


Usage
-----

See the sample projects and the documentation.


Support
-------

If you find any problems with the module or have suggestions for improvements, please
[file an issue](https://github.com/pegli/TiCarousel/issues) on Github.